Cell["\<\
As the Hadamard, quadrant, octant, and CNOT gates form a universal set of \
gates (to an arbitrary accuracy), it is interesting to see how these gates \
implement the Toffoli gate:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->2040007616,ExpressionUUID->"8a28e4aa-5b1f-493f-a07a-3c703abe7fe8"],

